" Avro schema for sales order event (schema registry)
{
  "namespace": "sap.s4.salesorder",
  "type": "record",
  "name": "SalesOrderChanged",
  "fields": [
    {"name": "salesOrderId", "type": "string"},
    {"name": "customerId", "type": "string"},
    {"name": "totalAmount", "type": "double"},
    {"name": "currency", "type": "string", "default": "USD"},
    {"name": "status", "type": {
      "type": "enum",
      "name": "OrderStatus",
      "symbols": ["NEW", "PENDING", "APPROVED", "REJECTED", "CANCELLED"]
    }},
    {"name": "items", "type": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "record",
        "name": "OrderItem",
        "fields": [
          {"name": "itemId", "type": "int"},
          {"name": "product", "type": "string"},
          {"name": "quantity", "type": "int"},
          {"name": "price", "type": "double"}
        ]
      }
    }}
  ]
}
"
" Schema evolution — backward compatible:
" Add optional fields only, never remove or rename
" Breaking change = new major topic (v3)

" SAP outbound connector: IDoc -> CloudEvents
" ALE change pointer captures document changes
" Background job sends to Event Mesh via RFC bridge

" Connector config (pseudocode):
connector = {
  "name": "sap-sd-order-outbound-v1",
  "type": "sap-outbound",
  "config": {
    "source": {
      "protocol": "RFC",
      "system": "S4H_PROD",
      "client": "100",
      "object": "SALESORDER",
      "change_pointer": "BDCP",
      "batch_size": 100,
      "poll_interval_ms": 5000
    },
    "target": {
      "topic": "sap.sd.salesorder",
      "format": "cloudEvents+json",
      "compression": "gzip"
    },
    "error_handling": {
      "max_retries": 3,
      "dead_letter_topic": "sap.dlq",
      "circuit_breaker": {
        "failure_threshold": 10,
        "reset_timeout_ms": 30000
      }
    }
  }
}
